elements.name: Adding a product to the cart

steps.name: I have navigated to the TutorialsNinja homepage
I enter a valid product name "Samsung Galaxy" in the search bar
I initiate the product search clicking on the search button
I should see a list of products related to the search term in the product search
I click on the add to cart button for "Samsung Galaxy"
I should see the product added successfully to the cart message
I click on the checkout button
